        "# RESPONSIBLE AI & MODEL INTERPRETATION\n",
        "\n",
        "## Project Report\n",
        "\n",
        "### Submitted By\n",
        "Name: NADIKOPPU BHAVANI\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 1. Introduction\n",
        "\n",
        "Responsible Artificial Intelligence (Responsible AI) ensures that AI systems are transparent, fair, interpretable, and unbiased. As AI models are increasingly used in real-world applications, understanding how predictions are made becomes very important.\n",
        "\n",
        "This project demonstrates Responsible AI techniques using model explainability and fairness analysis. LIME (Local Interpretable Model-Agnostic Explanations) was used to interpret predictions and identify important features affecting model decisions.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 2. Objectives\n",
        "\n",
        "The main objectives of this project are:\n",
        "\n",
        "- Analyze model explainability using LIME\n",
        "- Identify important features influencing predictions\n",
        "- Detect possible bias across sensitive groups\n",
        "- Evaluate fairness of the model\n",
        "- Recommend mitigation techniques\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 3. Technologies Used\n",
        "\n",
        "- Python\n",
        "- Scikit-learn\n",
        "- NumPy\n",
        "- Pandas\n",
        "- Matplotlib\n",
        "- LIME\n",
        "- Google Colab\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 4. Dataset Description\n",
        "\n",
        "The dataset contains features such as:\n",
        "\n",
        "- Age\n",
        "- Gender\n",
        "- Income\n",
        "\n",
        "The target variable predicts:\n",
        "- Class 0\n",
        "- Class 1\n",
        "\n",
        "Sensitive attributes like Gender were used for fairness analysis.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 5. Methodology\n",
        "\n",
        "## 5.1 Data Preprocessing\n",
        "\n",
        "The dataset was cleaned and transformed before training. Numerical values were normalized and categorical values were encoded.\n",
        "\n",
        "## 5.2 Model Training\n",
        "\n",
        "A machine learning classification model was trained using Scikit-learn algorithms.\n",
        "\n",
        "## 5.3 Explainability Using LIME\n",
        "\n",
        "LIME was used to generate local explanations for individual predictions and identify the important features influencing the model.\n",
        "\n",
        "## 5.4 Bias Analysis\n",
        "\n",
        "The model performance was evaluated separately for Male and Female groups to identify fairness differences.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 6. LIME Explainability Results\n",
        "\n",
        "The LIME explanation identified the following important features:\n",
        "\n",
        "- Age\n",
        "- Gender_Male\n",
        "- Income\n",
        "\n",
        "Prediction Probabilities:\n",
        "- Class 0: 0.37\n",
        "- Class 1: 0.63\n",
        "\n",
        "The results indicate that Age and Gender significantly influence model predictions.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 7. Bias Analysis Results\n",
        "\n",
        "## Male Group Performance\n",
        "\n",
        "| Metric | Value |\n",
        "|---|---|\n",
        "| Accuracy | 0.56 |\n",
        "| Macro Avg F1-Score | 0.56 |\n",
        "\n",
        "## Female Group Performance\n",
        "\n",
        "| Metric | Value |\n",
        "|---|---|\n",
        "| Accuracy | 0.49 |\n",
        "| Macro Avg F1-Score | 0.49 |\n",
        "\n",
        "The performance difference between groups indicates possible model bias.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 8. Mitigation Recommendations\n",
        "\n",
        "The following steps are recommended to improve fairness:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Balance the dataset across sensitive groups\n",
        "2. Remove biased proxy variables\n",
        "3. Add more diverse data samples\n",
        "4. Perform regular fairness testing\n",
        "5. Retrain the model with unbiased samples\n",
        "\n",
